scuba --e="SELECT
    SUM(1, sample_weight) AS agg0,
    COUNT(1),
    AVG( cpu_time_ns , COALESCE(sample_rate, weight)) AS  agg1 ,
     operator_type  AS  optype ,
     input_dims  AS  inputs ,
     output_dims  AS outputs,
     arguments AS args
FROM
     caffe2_operator_stats
WHERE
    1534429960 <=  time
    AND  time  <= 1534440759
    AND (
        ( operator_type ) IN (
            'Conv',
            'ConvTranspose',
            'FC',
            'FbFCPacked',
            'FCTransposed',
          )
    )
    and arguments is not null
    and arguments != '{}'
    and arguments != 'null'

GROUP BY
     optype ,
     inputs ,
     outputs ,
     args
ORDER BY
     agg1  DESC
LIMIT
    10000" --format=csv
